data.description: NEW CONSTRUCTION in Enclaves of Woodmont Country Club. Welcome to your luxurious, spacious, open concept home on the first hole of the golf course. The Citrus Grove model has 5 bedrooms including the primary suite looking out to the golf course and a second bedroom on the main floor. As you walk upstairs there are 3 bedrooms and large den/family room perfect for guests. The chef's dream kitchen has shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, large island, new SS appliances and large pantry. Enjoy outdoor entertaining in the screened patio looking to the lush golf course landscaping. The Woodmont CC is a newly built and non-mandatory golf course membership with a large pool, bar/restaurant, tennis courts and full fitness center. Other upgrades include motorized blinds, plantations shutters, epoxi garage with AC and insulation for a home gym, oversized laundry room and closets throughout. New Furniture is negotiable.
